{"data":[{"id":561767883,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"959df776b9ad5d55043cf942a0424832","url_token":"miji100","name":"水陌轻寒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58ef481c290cf9580a5efcc926c8c5a5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58ef481c290cf9580a5efcc926c8c5a5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/959df776b9ad5d55043cf942a0424832","user_type":"people","headline":"也许我们明天就相遇，也许只能在两个宇宙里平行~","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561767883","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545998209,"updated_time":1545998209,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫被证明了，题主立功了！他继承了民科的光荣的传统。高斯、伽罗华、欧拉、拉格朗日在这一刻灵魂附体！题主代表了民科悠久的历史和传统，在这一刻他不是一个人在战斗，他不是一个人！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560396125,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c5afca4748da16306298ab39f53fe830","url_token":"da-li-ya-wo-bo-yi","name":"达莉娅沃波依","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549ed9bfe1448bc096e8d4993312bda3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549ed9bfe1448bc096e8d4993312bda3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c5afca4748da16306298ab39f53fe830","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560396125","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545834496,"updated_time":1545834496,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":15,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不要害怕别人说什么，有梦就去追\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很大程度上众人都是抱着看笑话的心态来的，我也一样，但很不幸的是数学这门学科从初等到高等，发展的历史上充斥着偶然性，我怕你真的才华横溢别的不怎么行，偏偏把哥猜给试出来了，这就搞得我们很尴尬，岂不是打脸了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以呢，大家都在看着，你1月1号证出个啥，如果证成了，那别说清北了，哈佛mit绝大多数数学教授在你面前就是个弟弟。可你要证失败了，那就是成民科了，劝你老早回去继续复习，清北真的只是由高考分数决定的，而证实这种东西需要的天才和努力是任何大学都没法比的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可你要是在营销涨粉，我十几个知乎号到时候追着喷的你 都不认识\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559820267,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"22013139469948a48a6983a22b362c3c","url_token":"bj365","name":"空一格","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-16bff4cd9b634f213e42a85d121b3c86_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-16bff4cd9b634f213e42a85d121b3c86_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/22013139469948a48a6983a22b362c3c","user_type":"people","headline":"科技创造财富，知识点亮人生。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559820267","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545785674,"updated_time":1545785674,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":32,"content":"\u003cp\u003e酿希匹，别说保送清华北大上研了，当教授都没问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别说在清北当教授了，哈佛数学系都要过来挖你！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e诺贝尔奖里没有数学奖，但是数学有\u003cb\u003e费尔兹奖\u003c/b\u003e啊！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前些年有个俄罗斯怪才证明了庞加莱猜想，被授予了费尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你要是证明了哥德巴赫猜想，给你授三次费尔兹奖也不为过啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你即使得了一次费尔兹奖，你这倍子直接拿下了，还保什么送啊？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560956691,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560956691","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545902024,"updated_time":1545902024,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":20,"content":"\u003cp\u003e小朋友，保送北大清华比证明哥德巴赫猜想容易了N个数量级。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是保送北大的，十多年前了，那会只要你是数学OR物理竞赛集训队的，保送的时候跟招生老师说选北大数学系是没什么压力的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e竞赛想进集训队然后保送清北需要做到什么，两年学完高中所有课程+学完大学专业课+刷茫茫多的竞赛题+一个还算聪明的脑子。想学完这些，基本都是没什么休息时间的，寒暑假周末大半时间都要留校，每天六点起床到11点半睡觉也基本都是看书学习的。虽然艰难，但只要你不笨，而且特别能吃苦爱学习对数理充满兴趣，都还是有希望的。但我从来没觉得自己有生之年能触及那些能在历史长河中留下名字的人的地步，认真体会过就能发现天赋之间的差距几乎是一眼望去看不到顶的绝望。你需要比能保送清北的人平均水平远远超出许多的绝顶天赋+数十年如一日艰苦做科研的心性，也仅仅是有一点希望和可能去获得上帝给与的那一点灵光一闪，解决一些现在这些未曾解决的世界难题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上清北，你所面对的不过是从全国数百万应届考生中选出几百个这种万分之一的几率而已。这个概率是不大，但对于一般人都是有希望的。但想想证明哥德巴赫猜想那你要竞争的是人类历史上三百多年来所有天赋卓绝的人，说实在的，除非你发现你从小到大都表现的跟超级天才一样，从来没有一个能难得住你的数学问题，不然这个几率就是0.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561297093,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e26034c914d0115722adf3c211325ef0","url_token":"sanshiliuhaoji","name":"Trihexium","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e26034c914d0115722adf3c211325ef0","user_type":"people","headline":"36","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561297093","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545955505,"updated_time":1545955505,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e别说高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想了，有的初中生什么都没证出来也能上清华的\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559717513,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"60fc433e9e2a3c74d1cb8091a3a4b66a","url_token":"wu-hen-65-60","name":"吴痕","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6278d5b94f80ac775d15ca5494850006_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6278d5b94f80ac775d15ca5494850006_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/60fc433e9e2a3c74d1cb8091a3a4b66a","user_type":"people","headline":"爱买小米产品，容易闲扯辨舌，心态厄尔尼诺","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559717513","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545754519,"updated_time":1545754519,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前提是：\u003cb\u003e真的证明了\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果有高中生做到了，那么他的论文深度已经足以保证他的数学功底能够满足“XX大学数学系”的要求。任何成果都不是无本之木，若干年前的年纪轻轻就为群论做出开拓性成果的伽罗瓦同志，也不是自己端着一堆初等数学教材在那里玩玄学，人家可是学习了大量的高等数学知识（只是人家掌握有点快……）。因此如果存在这样牛逼的高中生，他的成果大概率不是在一堆初高中数学课本中达成的，而是来自于提前掌握了非常高端的数学工具，甚至洞悉当前数论研究的前沿。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或者非要说是不世出的天才一个人凭借初等数学知识推出来一个媲美现代数学的理论体系，这个……开心就好。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559993656,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bdc4123e8980c20b2109e00619d8fbea","url_token":"chen-xiang-yu-99-80","name":"陈向隅","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-feed5f9947f12a2bdd3e5c906597c1ef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-feed5f9947f12a2bdd3e5c906597c1ef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bdc4123e8980c20b2109e00619d8fbea","user_type":"people","headline":"我们背抵黑暗，只为守护光明。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559993656","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4fcc3098aef43f4cccc0193a77dd7b77_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545799965,"updated_time":1545799972,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":61,"content":"\u003cp\u003e作为一个纯天然无添加的数学白痴，我甚至去悄咪咪百度了一下啥是哥德巴赫.......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0107783cb5736be4d2306b34445e92b8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"120\" data-rawheight=\"120\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"120\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='120'%20height='120'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"120\" data-rawheight=\"120\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"120\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0107783cb5736be4d2306b34445e92b8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然鹅这并没有什么卵用因为我压根就没看懂百度百科到底在说啥。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4fcc3098aef43f4cccc0193a77dd7b77_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"214\" data-rawheight=\"154\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"214\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='214'%20height='154'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"214\" data-rawheight=\"154\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"214\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4fcc3098aef43f4cccc0193a77dd7b77_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是jio得吧，既然答主都能想着去证明它了，那数学起码还是不错的。就算到时候真的证明失败也没关系，上个211什么的一样可以继续追梦嘛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然还是要祝福一下，毕竟万一真的证明了，全世界的数学家可以少掉多少根头发啊。23333。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b312de00b55a0b3a3fb19f780bb836a4_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"124\" data-rawheight=\"116\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"124\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='124'%20height='116'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"124\" data-rawheight=\"116\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"124\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b312de00b55a0b3a3fb19f780bb836a4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561706884,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561706884","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545991223,"updated_time":1545991223,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我是这位假装是老师的作家的老师，在此向各位知友道歉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e出于对网络暴力的考虑，恕我不能说明该作家的姓名和工作单位。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事情是这样的，我在他们入行的时候就给他们介绍了怎样编出一个好故事，似乎就是那时候开始引起他的兴趣的。我们单位有写作培训，但是写作培训是只给天资聪慧的作家办的，他不是个很有名气的作家，但是他在编故事方面有挺高的造诣，特别是对情景代入这一方面下了苦功夫，很多时候写作他都会提出多一种写作方案。而且他自己去找培训老师谈，旁听写作培训，真的是很上进的作家。培训老师在办公室也经常会说他有想法，不囿于定势思维。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大约是一个月前，他拿了一页纸给我，说他有了写一个前无古人后无来者好故事的思路，我开始还很惊奇，他写的思路有些东西我也看不懂，我认为是不可能有一个普通作家能另辟蹊径的，但是我觉得作为老师不能给学生泼冷水，所以也就说了几句鼓励的话，告诉他有想法总比没想法的好。然后前几天他突然告诉我他已经完成了那个故事，我虽然不相信，但我还是看了一下他写的内容，怎么说呢，有一些部分我不太明白，因为这些不是写作范畴的内容，有点类似欺诈，给他人随便下定义。但是培训老师也看过了，他的意思就是这是一篇浮在表面上的文章，大部分没有问题，但是对于一些真正说明问题的细节点，却是很模糊地一笔带过，严格的来说，不算是一个真正有逻辑的故事。单位里对他的故事都传遍了，甚至他都是个风云人物了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过他似乎无法理解自己究竟哪里写的不好，一直坚信自己没有问题。他在知乎上回答这个问题，其实他不是一个骗赞和消费大众善意的人，只是有时有点不甘心，因为他除了写作其他都是一团糟，买房都有困难，但是他觉得这个社会对于有特长的人很不公平，其实不非得是前无古人后无来者，就算是本畅销书就行了，可是他目前的能力连这点小要求都满足不了，所以才有了在知乎上发故事的想法，希望各位可以理解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e关于匿名在知乎发表这个故事的事，我是反对过他了，但是毕竟这也是他的自由，而且我作为老师知识实在是有限，也不能完全说服他就是错的。在这里只能跟大家道个歉，解释一下，他其实不是一个投机取巧之辈，他只是年轻气盛有点心高气傲罢了。我希望各位知友嘴下留情，不要使用网络暴力，不要人肉搜索。不管他是对是错，不要用狠毒的言语打翻了一个作家对写作编故事热爱的心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e谢谢大家了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561366667,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9537d5520b80eef1771e7bfef8982381","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561366667","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545962477,"updated_time":1545962477,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不光会被清北保送 而且还会拿菲尔兹奖 可能开辟了新的数学方向 改写数学史 连带着数学的n个分支的发展 还有终身教授 金钱荣誉地位 走向人生巅峰 成为历史人物！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557774031,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fbc1661039fe84e3d0eae8ee359d98e5","url_token":"reciprocity","name":"Reciprocity","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fbc1661039fe84e3d0eae8ee359d98e5","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557774031","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545527876,"updated_time":1545527876,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":22,"content":"\u003cp\u003e1. 如果你只用初等数论知识完成的证明，建议放弃。因为证明错的概率是99.999999%，话说回来，即使你的证明没有问题，一个很严肃的问题是你很难找到一个大学数学老师来花时间验证这个东西。民科或许愿意，但民科一样无法获得主流学术界的认同。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. 如果你的英文还可以，建议将其翻译成英文，挂在arxiv上。挂上去之后你对这个享有完全的著作权，不必担心抄袭问题，同时向国际顶级期刊投稿，如Ann. Math, JAMS, Acta Math等等。怀尔斯的费马大定理的证明就是在Ann. Math. 上发表的哦。一旦在这种期刊上发表，就宣告了你的证明的正确性。而不是像其他答主贴图一样，发表在国内水杂志上，并没有任何卵用\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560474011,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aea5bb74cdc9c44e0b2b6a450a870459","url_token":"zhi-zhang-shao-nian-55-68","name":"起个名真费劲","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aea5bb74cdc9c44e0b2b6a450a870459","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560474011","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545840654,"updated_time":1545840898,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":49,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管题主是否证明出了哥德巴赫猜想，都会有人支持你，因为谁没年少轻狂过，你还年轻，有的是可能，有的是时间。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的证明正确，皆大欢喜，如果你的证明不正确，希望你也不要放弃对数学的热爱，毕竟冰冷的高山，不是那么好爬。愿你以后再回想当初的自己，能不悔当初，一笑了之\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e来自一个知乎小透明的首次长(？)答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e求轻喷\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感激不尽\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563132077,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created"