你的问题在于读书不多而想得太多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e------------------------------分割线---------------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这种钓鱼贴就应该让他沉下去。这种问题简直就是对学数学的人的侮辱，居然还要1.1号在知乎公开论文。哪里冒出来的民科，真的够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e给你一句名言：too young too simple sometimes naive\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563499246,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"43661a9de5d28361a121bb261afb364e","url_token":"yan-wang-da-ren-jiao-judy","name":"燕王大人叫Judy","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e35537f8ea569bd6343b939f97d875a8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e35537f8ea569bd6343b939f97d875a8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/43661a9de5d28361a121bb261afb364e","user_type":"people","headline":"滑铁卢大学数学狗/章圈咸鱼鹤声","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563499246","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546243853,"updated_time":1546243853,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e啧啧 赶紧过来留句话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e万一明天真论文发表了，那本人可就是在知乎回答过证明哥德巴赫猜想的天才的问题的人了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563423050,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563423050","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546235427,"updated_time":1546235740,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e微分不是积分，极值不是最值。 泰勒展开比洛必达公式好用，我用泰勒从28项展开到82项，我太了解他了！ 我刚刚进来的时候，有个学生就问我，sin|x|函数的图像怎么画啊？我们说一个数学考试没有自己的公式是可悲的，有了公式还不去用就是可耻的。年轻的考生还在笑，我是笑不出来。有的考生一看到题，第一反应“哇，太难了！”这怎么行呢？见到难题，尤其需要乐观向上。经常有小朋友过来问我，洛必达法则到底有几个条件啊？我看有些教材，洛必达竟然和拉格朗日谈起了恋爱，洛必达叫拉格朗日叫日日，拉格朗日叫洛必达叫达达，求导不分，积分颠倒。这样的教材主创人员是要向全国人民谢罪的！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有些考生竟然还带了两张准考证，结果一进考场就被拦下来了。你说你要证哥德巴赫猜想，有本事上台来我们俩比划比划。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是身经百战见得多了，我研究了十七年的高数，每年稿费不到70元，十七年下来不到2000元。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=160\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=120\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
